    'gamecenter.battleball.description': "BattleBall is a colorful game where you have to color more surfaces than your opponent. Items appear randomly and give you unique powers to boost your chances. Tactics, skill and quick decisions are the key to victory. Will you become the BattleBall champion?",
    'gamecenter.tombrunner.description': "This treasure hunter is determined to find as many ancient coins as possible while running through age-old corridors and jumping over huge cracks. On your journey through this endless 3D running game you'll also come across unstable, fragile bridges. Find out how long you can survive.",
    'gamecenter.flappybirds.description': "Flappy Bird is an arcade-style game where we control the little bird Faby, who moves to the right. Your task is to guide Faby through the pipes, which have equal gaps placed at random heights.",
    'gamecenter.bargame.description': "Show off your skills by working in the hotel's best bar and serving the finest drinks to the most demanding customers. Try to be the waiter with the best skills, delivering the glasses to win the game and prove your cocktail talent.",
    'gamecenter.roombuildergame.description': "Are you good at building rooms? Do you have enough imagination? Take on the challenge and build a themed room in less than 6 minutes. The nicest room wins!",
